title: "chore: 2026-07-06 ecosystem audit #13 — Semgrep-issue metadata backfill, scale-out initiative pm-9rxu, composability contract set"
description: "Third same-day audit (follows #11 morning, #12 evening; session item pm-3rgp). Full all-status review at 1621 items: commits dc0dc252/00d01c69/9c909a58 map 1:1 to items (audit-12 batch, pm-6e1d, pm-rjqr); no GH issue newer than 474; zero open orphans. Gaps found and fixed this session: (1) 40 Semgrep finding Issues + batch pm-oz8u were active without AC/estimate — backfilled per-finding AC referencing the Semgrep ID and location; (2) pm-doxj capability index was missing pm-qwoy; (3) no tracker home existed for the stated scale goal (100k-1M items, thousands of agents) — created initiative epic pm-9rxu + ADR pm-bl8x + 7 children (pm-mi2x/pm-801d/pm-dfg0/pm-0qg5/pm-lvyd/pm-o79o/pm-g2zz); (4) no tracker home for the grep/jq composability principle — created pm-m9xv story + pm-646c NDJSON + pm-psy1 scripting contract under pm-mpbb; (5) recorded long-term horizon ordering (near/mid/long) on pm-doxj. Verified healthy without changes: pm-n7rr and pm-usfg initiative trees (the requested simplification + SDK-first brainstorms already fully materialized, 64/64 commands and 8/8 SDK domains covered)."
