notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-06T21:26:56.685Z",maintainer-agent,"Strategic layer completed this session: initiatives now number three (pm-n7rr simplification, pm-usfg SDK-first, pm-9rxu scale-out) plus the composability contract set (pm-m9xv/pm-646c/pm-psy1). Horizon ordering recorded on pm-doxj: near = simplification+SDK-first, mid = composability + code-scanning zero-findings, long = scale-out (implementation deliberately behind the SDK-first primitive layer). Dedupe evidence: scalability/sharding/pagination/ndjson/xargs/exit-code searches all returned only unrelated closed items before creation."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-06T21:26:56.283Z",maintainer-agent,"Audit #13 gotchas: (1) pm list --status ... --format json | jq length returned 6 for ~150 rows — never count actives from list --json; use the table output or per-id gets. (2) validate --json (not --format json) exposes .checks[].details.missing_acceptance_criteria_item_ids / missing_estimated_minutes_item_ids — exact backfill worklists, truncation-flagged. (3) Per-finding scanner Issues created by batch import land without AC/estimate — future scanner-import batches should seed AC/estimate at creation time (pattern: remediate-or-suppress + rescan-clean + gates-green)."
close_reason: "Audit #13 complete: 41 Semgrep-item metadata backfills; roadmap index fixed (pm-qwoy); third initiative pm-9rxu (scale to 1M items / 1000s agents, ADR pm-bl8x, 7 children); composability set pm-m9xv/pm-646c/pm-psy1; horizon plan on pm-doxj; validate/health green, zero open orphans"
